Package: nonmemtools
Type: Package
Title: R Tools for NONMEM PK/PD Dataset Preparation from CDISC SDTM
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2025-12-23
Authors@R: person(
    given = "Christian",
    family = "Baghai",
    email = "christian.baghai@outlook.fr",
    role = c("aut", "cre"),
    comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0000-0000-0000")
  )
Description: Provides tools for converting CDISC SDTM pharmacokinetic data 
    (PC, EX, DM domains) into NONMEM-ready datasets. Includes comprehensive
    quality control validation, PK parameter calculations, and standardized
    workflows for population pharmacokinetic analysis. Designed for clinical
    statistical programmers working in pharmacometrics and drug development.
